Reasoning: The paper discusses the trade-off between modularity and efficiency in programs operating on collections, which is a common concern in programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed solution involves a deep embedding of the Scala collections API, which is related to database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed solution by re-implementing code analyses, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
